 "body": "<p>A deduction in computing the profits of a trade carried on by an individual (either alone or in a partnership of individuals) is allowed for certain revenue expenditure incurred to meet a special security threat arising from the trade. The deduction applies to Income Tax only.</p>\n\n<p>The guidance on the application of the deduction is arranged as follows:</p>\n",
